  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@bobylito @redox currently is impossible to use external plugins which relies on _data-_ attributes for configuration. An example is [Masonry](http://masonry.desandro.com/) (see also issue #736).\n\nRight now the only _clean_ way to achieve this is to write a custom widgets which basically wraps the hits one. I think it could make sense to add an esclusive `items` template property to override the inner react map.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-12-15T10:30:28Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/707#issuecomment-164718277",
    "id": 164718277,
