    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think the idea fits the `hits` widget scope. This is an advanced option because users will then have to handle everything themselves, but I see how this can be useful.\n\nRegarding Masonry, I'm not sure a jQuery plugin that reorders DOM elements (if that's what it's doing) will play well with React, though.\n",
